        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段跟跌 恒指挫564點報22638點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國公布關稅細節後引發全球股市動盪，港股今早亦跟隨外圍急回。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250402_FI_source-ap_US_tariffs_on_cars_25091360163324.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250402_FI_source-ap_US_tariffs_on_cars_25091360163324.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數開市報22638點，跌564點或2.43%。恒生科技指數開報5257點，跌168點或3.11%；國企指數以8312點開市，跌219點或2.57%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍向下，上季再斥6億美元於美國市場回購的阿里巴巴(09988)，今早開報122.5元，跌5.77%；騰訊(00700)開報493元，跌2.18%；美團(03690)開報152.4元，跌3.42%。滙控(00005)開報87.45元，跌0.63%；友邦(01299)開報59元，跌1.99%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240416_FI_source-web_01810-SU7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240416_FI_source-web_01810-SU7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">連續兩日表現在藍籌包尾的小米(01810)，今早開報43.8元，跌1.68%。內地車企龍頭比亞迪(01211)開報375.6元，跌1.52%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14826803-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%9f%e8%b7%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab564%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122638%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKS_source-bp_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 09:25:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英皇澄天再錄成交  一房單位成交價513萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14826001&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英皇地產港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」高層海景戶推售，今再錄得投資客入市，成交單位為一房的25樓B室，成交價513萬，實用面積287平方呎，成交呎價17875。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">買家為外區投資者，特別鍾情項目擁開揚海景景致，加上有見租金回報較銀行定存吸引，租金走勢持續向上，故購入單位作長綫收租用途。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「澄天」至今已售出98伙，佔整體項目近9成，合共套現逾港幣6億。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14826001-%e8%8b%b1%e7%9a%87%e6%be%84%e5%a4%a9%e5%86%8d%e9%8c%84%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e4%b8%80%e6%88%bf%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e5%83%b9513%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/pp_emperor_bp_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 09:21:06",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
